---
const {
  imageSrc = '/img/how-ai-agents.png',
  imageAlt = 'Laptop showing RSVPs being managed automatically'
} = Astro.props as {
  imageSrc?: string;
  imageAlt?: string;
};
---

<section class="relative w-full px-4 md:px-8 lg:px-20 py-16 lg:py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col gap-10 md:flex-row md:items-center md:gap-12">
    <div class="md:w-[40%]">
      <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-[#fffefe1a] bg-[#fffefe0d] backdrop-blur-sm">
        <img
          src={imageSrc}
          alt={imageAlt}
          loading="lazy"
          class="h-full w-full object-cover"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 md:w-[60%] text-center md:text-left">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold [font-family:'Segoe_UI_Symbol-Regular',Helvetica]">
        <span class="text-white">Helping Lorton </span>
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-[linear-gradient(90deg,#2b7fff_0%,#ac46ff_50%,#f6329a_100%)]">
          Businesses Every Day
        </span>
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#d0d5db] [font-family:'Segoe_UI_Symbol-Regular',Helvetica]">
        <p>
          At a community event in Laurel Hill Park, a vendor used our AI Agent to manage RSVPs. It handled over 200 responses in one afternoon â€“ saving them from hiring temporary staff.
        </p>
        <p>
          A bakery near Silverbrook Road was wasting hours every week answering "Are you open today?" on Facebook. Their AI Agent now handles that automatically, saving them 6+ hours per week.
        </p>
        <p>These are your neighbors. Your community. Local businesses just like yours that were losing money to missed leads.
</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

